C_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"cycling fans\", \"from\": 4280, \"to\": 4292}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4315, \"to\": 4327}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The BBC only has rights to broadcast two streams at any one time, however, so while the track cycling will be heavily favoured by the national broadcaster, it's not guaranteed that every round of the Team Sprint will be shown.\", \"from\": 4387, \"to\": 4613, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4391, \"end\": 4394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9999044853605185, \"rank\": 9.551909594677423e-05, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 4587, \"end\": 4598, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_sprint\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2779454546500683e-23, \"text\": \"Team Sprint\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_sprint\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_sprint\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"rights\", \"from\": 4404, \"to\": 4410}, {\"ngram\": \"two streams\", \"from\": 4424, \"to\": 4435}, {\"ngram\": \"any one time\", \"from\": 4439, \"to\": 4451}, {\"ngram\": \"the track cycling\", \"from\": 4471, \"to\": 4488}, {\"ngram\": \"the national broadcaster\", \"from\": 4517, \"to\": 4541}, {\"ngram\": \"every round\", \"from\": 4568, \"to\": 4579}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For that, you will have to watch onDiscovery+, home to the most comprehensive coverage in the UK - 3,800 hours of live action across 55 channels.\", \"from\": 4615, \"to\": 4760, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4709, \"end\": 4711, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999999326974, \"rank\": 3.4348604323236384e-11, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\",