ly the most comprehensive free Olympics coverage in the world.\", \"from\": 5110, \"to\": 5279, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5113, \"end\": 5122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999999999940883, \"rank\": 4.782006243888288e-12, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"cycling fans\", \"from\": 5124, \"to\": 5136}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 5147, \"to\": 5159}, {\"ngram\": \"9and its9Now streaming\", \"from\": 5179, \"to\": 5201}, {\"ngram\": \"arguably the most comprehensive free Olympics coverage\", \"from\": 5211, \"to\": 5265}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 5269, \"to\": 5278}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As is the case in other territories, a good chunk of the action is expected to be included in live television broadcast, but for guaranteed coverage of all the Team Sprint racing, fans can head to 9Now on the smart device of their choosing.\", \"from\": 5281, \"to\": 5521, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the case\", \"from\": 5287, \"to\": 5295}, {\"ngram\": \"other territories\", \"from\": 5299, \"to\": 5316}, {\"ngram\": \"a good chunk\", \"from\": 5318, \"to\": 5330}, {\"ngram\": \"the action\", \"from\": 5334, \"to\": 5344}, {\"ngram\": \"live television broadcast\", \"from\": 5375, \"to\": 5400}, {\"ngram\": \"guaranteed coverage\", \"from\": 5410, \"to\": 5429}, {\"ngram\": \"all the Team Sprint racing\", \"from\": 5433, \"to\": 5459}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 5461, \"to\": 5465}, {\"ngram\": \"9Now\", \"from\": 5478, \"to\": 5482}, {\"ngram\": \"the smart device\", \"from\": 5486, \"to\": 5502}, {\"ngram\": \"their choosing\", \"from\": 5506, \"to\": 5520}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you are traveling abroad and try to access your usual live streaming services to watch the action, you may find your access to be geo-restricted.\", \"from\":